        <obo:IAO_0000231>The term anxious withdrawal (or anxious solitude) is better suited in a more specific domain ontology, such as PHASES.</obo:IAO_0000231>
        <obo:IAO_0000589 xml:lang="en">anxious withdrawal triat characteristic (EMRO)</obo:IAO_0000589>
